data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in the exclusive gated community of Capri in Isles of Oasis! This home is perfect for entertaining. Downstairs features a fantastic open living room off the oversized kitchen, and a wonderful view to large gated backyard! Kitchen is updated with tons of storage and counter space. All 4 bedrooms are upstairs, and you’ll be blown away by the storage options and wonderful layout. This gated community is in a fabulous location in Homestead and boasts access to a state of the art clubhouse with pool, gym, and splash pad!
